# Bundled llama-server runtime drop point.
#
# Empty in the repo. The Release workflow fetches a pinned llama.cpp build into
# this directory (the llama-server binary + its shared libraries) so it gets
# bundled as a Tauri resource (see tauri.conf.json `bundle.resources`). At
# runtime the app unpacks it into the app-data `bin/` on first use.
#
# Everything here except this file is gitignored — never commit the binaries.
